  "remarks": "Judge of the Supreme Court. A former Judge of the Minsk Moskovski District Court and currently judge of the Supreme Court. He sentenced the former presidential candidate, Alyaksandr Kazulin, to five-and-a-half years in jail for organising protests in March 2006 against the fraudulent elections.The way he conducted the trial was a clear violation of the Code of Criminal Procedure.",
